description: This file defines external API functions and data structures for ASN.1 'OtherName' and 'OtherString' objects related to ASN.1 encoding/decoding, specifically in the context of ASN.1 object handling within the project. It provides factory functions for creating ASN.1 object representations.

methods.name: AnscAsn1CreateOtherName
methods.description: Factory function to create a new ASN.1 'OtherName' object handle.

methods.name: AnscAsn1CreateOtherString
methods.description: Factory function to create a new ASN.1 'OtherString' object handle.
